    "body": "Any news?\r\n\r\nI have a similar issue, just with a black screen instead of glitches: https://github.com/OpenRA/OpenRA/issues/11314\r\n\r\nthe first time i ran it, i got to the mod selection and from there to the games without any issues.\r\n\r\nSince then, whenever I run it in fullscreen, all I see is the cursor of the mod selection, or whichever mod I run; only black screen other than the cursor, though. Sound seems to be fine, as do buttons to interact.\r\n\r\nWindow mode runs without issue.\r\n\r\nIssue not affected by wether I run the game using the nvidia card, or only cpu."
